                  Muhammad Luqman Fikri and
                  Jiale Wu and
                  Jie Li and
                  Lei Zhong and
                  Yusheng Ji},
	title = {Blockchain-based Edge-assisted Knowledge Base Management for Semantic
                  Communication in Remote Driving},
